{"tid":721229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國名企破產 被揭涉「中國式造假」","createTime":"2018-06-28T14:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T23:20:04.000Z","uid":53379,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8003ef2a541fc99b8da600e5f41b5a09954d12b2","tid":721229,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"【中國名企破產 被揭涉「中國式造假」】<br />\n【「漢芯事件」2.0】<br />\n<br />\n中國山東常林機械集團，曾經多次被列入「中國機械工業百強」，累積收過國家15億元的科研資助。<br />\n<br />\n不過最近就被員工揭發，常林的科研項目涉嫌造假，出現「漢芯事件」2.0。<span style=\"color: red;\">常林一直聲稱掌握液壓產品的核心技術，但有員工指常林出產其中一款液壓泵，只是將日本川畸的液壓泵表面油漆磨走，再換上常林自己的商標，這款液壓泵亦通過了國家鑑定</span>。<br />\n<br />\n除了產品造假，常林的賬目亦引起不少人質疑，一年內竟出現兩份財務報表，而且數據差距明顯。而從2014年開始，多家銀行因爲常林無法償還貸款，而拒絕再批准借貸申請。之後那年就爆發財務危機，拖欠員工薪金。在這幾年裡面，常林依然得到國家大額科研資助，直至年初正式破產倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1765136150297530/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1765136150297530%2F&d=TaoBu5I90RIq7Tx47wXr75zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=5f488175\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1765136150297530/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1532d96b4904dbf21425b50d9bec0de025536df","tid":721229,"uid":83582,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"「中國造假2025」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e146ce25cff33b2f4f7471da0c6fd32426c21cd4","tid":721229,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dbdca869c6424afd31e8fa44307e4079905d42","tid":721229,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":